name: Keith Ellison
tweet: @JoeBiden signing Emmett Till Antilynching Act is no cause for negative comparisons btwn Biden & Obama b/ it had to get thru both Houses of Congress before Biden could sign it. Let’s get folks to the polls in Nov 2022 so Biden can sign some more good bills.  What do you think?
